    Exception Description
    EmptyChapterNameException
    Exception for empty name field of class Chapter
    EmptyChapterWorldException
    Exception for empty world field of class Chapter
    EmptyCollectionException
    Exception for empty collection
    EmptyCoordinateYException
    Exception for empty y field of class Coordinates
    EmptyNameException
    Exception for empty name field of class SpaceMarine
    EmptyPathException
    Exception for empty filePath field of class FileManager
    IncorrectAnswerException
    Exception for entering a non-existent value (not 1 and not 2) while selecting for update
    IncorrectCommandException
    Exception for entering non-valid command
    IncorrectCoordinateXException
    Exception for entering x field value of class Coordinates, which is greater than 991
    IncorrectCoordinateYException
    Exception for entering y field value of class Coordinates, which is greater than 767
    IncorrectHealthException
    Exception for entering health field value of class SpaceMarine, which is lower or equals to 0
    IncorrectScriptInputException
    Exception for interactive communication with script
    NoGreaterElementException
    Exception if the collection does not have an element greater than the one entered
    NoLowerElementException
    Exception if the collection does not have an element lower than the one entered
    NoMatchException
    Exception if there is no collection elements with type SpaceMarine, with field achievements values starts with entered substring
    NullLastSaveException
    Exception for non-saved collection
    ObjectDoesNotExistException
    Exception when a collection element cannot be removed from a specified ID
    RecursionScriptException
    Exception for recursive script calling
    SpaceMarineNotFoundException
    Exception if an element with a specified ID does not appear in the collection
    WrongAmountOfElementsInCommandException
    Exception for calling a command with an invalid number of arguments
